Content: Automatically add the toggle sprint skill to summons.
The toggle sprint skill will be automatially added to party members. Not necessarily needed if you intend to always be sprinting.
Allow sprinting in combat. Sprinting does not affect movement AP costs, so this setting purely speeds up combat.
Allow enemies to sprint with their own speed settings.
Enable walk speed overrides for enemies. Not recommended since some enemies begin to slide at higher speeds (zombies).
[Debug] Enable to allow the setup dialog to trigger again when going into the Toggle Sprint dialog menu.
Enable to no longer display sprinting as a status. Recommended if you're also not using the toggle sprint skill.
Move at a much faster speed up ladders.
The speed at which the party moves when sprinting is enabled.
The speed at which the enemies move if enemy sprinting is enabled.
The speed at which the party moves when walking.
The speed at which enemies moves when walking, if enabled.
